# 🗄️ SQL & Data Analysis Fundamentals

## Overview

This project demonstrates the use of SQL to query, clean, modify, and analyse relational database data. Using core SQL techniques, I explored datasets by writing queries to retrieve information, handle missing values, transform data, and generate insights.

The project showcases essential SQL skills used in data analysis, including filtering, string matching, date and time manipulation, aggregate calculations, aliasing, subqueries, logical operators, NULL value handling, and modifying database records.

